---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Meter Networking | Blue Cap IT — Meter Partner" description="Blue Cap IT partners with Meter to deliver full-stack enterprise networking as a service. Custom-built hardware, AI-powered dashboard, ISP management, and hands-free network operations — all on a simple monthly subscription.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> Networking</div>
      <div class="section-label">Meter Partner</div>
      <h1>Enterprise Networking <span class="grad">Made Simple</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Blue Cap IT partners with Meter to deliver full-stack enterprise networking — purpose-built hardware, intelligent software, and hands-free operations — all as a service. No upfront hardware costs. No complexity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- METER LOGO -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding:2rem 1.5rem;">
      <img src="/meter/Meter-purple.png" alt="Meter" style="max-height:80px;width:auto;"/>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY METER -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why Meter</div>
          <h2>Network as a Service.<br/><span class="grad">Built for the Modern Enterprise.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Most businesses piece together networking from multiple vendors — buying hardware, hiring specialists, and juggling ISPs. Meter replaces all of that with one integrated solution: custom hardware, intelligent software, professional installation, and ongoing management, delivered as a simple monthly subscription.</p>
          <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top:1rem;">As a Meter Partner, Blue Cap IT designs, deploys, and manages your Meter network — so you get enterprise-grade connectivity without the enterprise-grade headaches.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Network Assessment</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🏗️</div>
            <div><h4>Full-Stack Solution</h4><p>Switches, access points, firewalls, gateways, software, installation, and ongoing management — all from one provider. No more multi-vendor complexity.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">💰</div>
            <div><h4>No Upfront Hardware Costs</h4><p>Meter owns the hardware. You pay a simple monthly subscription based on your square footage. Existing hardware buyback program available.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🤖</div>
            <div><h4>AI-Powered Management</h4><p>Meter Command uses generative AI to build custom dashboards, troubleshoot issues, and manage your network — all from a natural language interface.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon">🔧</div>
            <div><h4>Hands-Free Operations</h4><p>From ISP negotiations to network design to proactive monitoring — Meter handles the complexity so your team can focus on the business.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRODUCT LINES -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Meter Hardware &amp; Software</div>
        <h2>Purpose-Built.<br/><span class="grad">Fully Integrated.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0.8rem auto 0;text-align:center;">Meter designs and manufactures its own hardware and software — so every component works together seamlessly. Wi-Fi 7 ready, enterprise-grade, and managed for you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid">
        <a href="meter-switches.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <img src="/meter/hw-s-series.avif" alt="Meter S-Series Switches" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Switches</h3>
          <p>The S-Series: 24-port, 48-port, and core switches with PoE++, 2.5GbE, and 25Gbps uplinks. Silent operation and compact form factors built for modern offices.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="meter-access-points.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <img src="/meter/hw-a-series.avif" alt="Meter Access Points" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Access Points</h3>
          <p>Wi-Fi 7 tri-band access points with custom circuitry for strict radio isolation. The A1 for high-demand environments and A2 for hospitality — both delivering blazing-fast wireless.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="meter-firewalls.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <img src="/meter/hw-f-series.avif" alt="Meter F-Series Firewalls" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Firewalls</h3>
          <p>In-house designed firewalls with automatic failover, deep packet inspection, and seamless integration with every other Meter component. Enterprise security without the complexity.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="meter-gateway.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <img src="/meter/hw-p-series.avif" alt="Meter 5G Gateway" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>5G Gateway</h3>
          <p>Cellular connectivity with up to 1200Mbps over 5G. Provides ISP failover, out-of-band management, and reliable backup connectivity for critical sites.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="meter-dashboard.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <img src="/meter/dashboard-network.webp" alt="Meter Dashboard" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Meter Dashboard &amp; Command</h3>
          <p>AI-powered network management with natural language controls, real-time monitoring, custom dashboards, and collaborative tools. Ask a question — Command builds the answer.</p>
          <span class="pcard-arrow">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">How It Works</div>
        <h2>From Design to <span class="grad">Done</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0.8rem auto 0;text-align:center;">Meter handles every step of your network — from planning to installation to ongoing management. Here's how the process works.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));">
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">📐</div>
          <h3>1. Network Design</h3>
          <p>Meter's engineering team designs a custom network tailored to your space, devices, and performance requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🔌</div>
          <h3>2. Professional Install</h3>
          <p>Meter handles the full installation — hardware, cabling, configuration, and testing. No work required from your team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">🌐</div>
          <h3>3. ISP Management</h3>
          <p>Meter negotiates with ISPs, manages contracts, and handles all provider coordination so you don't have to.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon">📊</div>
          <h3>4. Ongoing Operations</h3>
          <p>Proactive monitoring, automatic updates, and expert support keep your network running at peak performance — 24/7.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
      <div class="section-label">Get Started</div>
      <h2>Ready to Upgrade <span class="grad">Your Network?</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="max-width:600px;margin:0.8rem auto 2rem;text-align:center;">Contact Blue Cap IT for a free network assessment. We'll evaluate your current setup and show you how Meter can simplify your networking — with zero upfront hardware costs.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Request a Free Assessment</a>
        <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
